==English==

===Etymology===
French and Old French '''machine''', from latinized Greek '''[[machina]]''', from [[w:Doric Greek|Doric Greek]] '''[[μαχανά]]''' (''makhana'') ([[Ionic Greek]] '''[[μηχανή]]''' ''[[mekhane]]'') "machine, tool", from [[μάχος]], [[μήχος]] (''makhos'', ''mekhos'') "device, assistance, way".

